--- !u!1001 &2092327246
PrefabInstance:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  serializedVersion: 2
  m_Modification:
    serializedVersion: 3
    m_TransformParent: {fileID: 0}
    m_Modifications:
    - target: {fileID: 321053737242813839, guid: 07a58fb99198d8f429d06902a541622e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_IsActive
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 564308043685198918, guid: 07a58fb99198d8f429d06902a541622e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'King: States how many subjects are next to them. If lying, will state
        two subjects if next to a ghost, and no subjects if not


        Executioner:
        the second character is a subject if and only if the first is a subject.
        If lying, the second character is always a ghost. If he picks himself, he
        is a ghost


        Nun: States two potential subjects the ghost could be.
        Will select multiple ghosts if possible, and will only select subjects if
        lying. If she picks herself, she is a lying subject


        Priest: Only
        one of three characters is a ghost. If lying, none of them are. If he picks
        himself, he is telling the truth


        Maid: States a character is a
        ghost. Will always select subjects if lying. If she picks herself, she is
        a lying subject'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 564308043685198918, guid: 07a58fb99198d8f429d06902a541622e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_fontSize
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 649765280201625091, guid: 07a58fb99198d8f429d06902a541622e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'Doctor: States an honest subject, lying subject and a ghost. If lying,
        will call a ghost a lying subject and a lying subject a ghost


        Blacksmith:
        States how far they are from the closest lying subject. If lying, states
        how far they are from the closest ghost


        Chef: States a character
        is telling the truth. Will select lying subjects if lying. Will never select
        ghosts


        ALL GHOSTS: Disguises as a random subject and gives false
        information


        <color=#ff3838>Phantom:</color> A subject next to me
        lies'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2122283977938353373, guid: 07a58fb99198d8f429d06902a541622e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_IsActive
      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6371304111096550638, guid: 07a58fb99198d8f429d06902a541622e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_IsActive
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7178253644178797337, guid: 07a58fb99198d8f429d06902a541622e, type: 3}
